== Access == * Rail: Approximately 20–25 minutes by bus from {{ill|Kurayoshi Station|ja|倉吉駅|12=draft|12=draft}} on the JR {{ill|San'in Main Line|ja|山陰本線|12=draft|12=draft}} via {{ill|Hinonmaru Bus|ja|日ノ丸自動車|lt=Hinonmaru Bus|lt_ja=日ノ丸バス|12=draft|12=draft}}. * Bus: Direct bus service for Misasa Onsen / Hawai Onsen. * By Car: Accessible via the {{ill|Sanyō Expressway|ja|山陰自動車道|12=draft|12=draft}} from the Hawai Interchange via National Route 179 and Tottori Prefecture Road 21 (Tottori-Kanago-Kurayoshi Line); alternatively, from the {{ill|Yonago Expressway|ja|米子自動車道|12=draft|12=draft}} via National Routes 313 and 482, National Route 179, and Tottori Prefecture Road 21.
